          <h1><span data-en>Contact Us</span><span data-zh>聯絡我們</span></h1>
          <p>
            <span data-en>Whether you have a question about our tradition, want to attend a class, or are interested in membership — reach out and we'll get back to you promptly.</span>
            <span data-zh>無論您想了解本會的道統傳承、參加課程，或有意申請入會，歡迎與我們聯絡，我們將盡快回覆。</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

